&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1329652/kuba-hasnt-forgotten-monica&quot; title=&quot;93,119 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Kuba hasn&apos;t forgotten Monica&lt;/a&gt;
